metadata.name: SLIMY Pre-Reveal
metadata.description: Slimy's are a unique collection of 4.444 NFT's, driven by the community (DAO). Holding your slimy gives you an exclusive access to the metaverse called slimy land, members of this land would get unique and valuable prizes, be owner of the metaverse! Also, every holder will get 3 evolutions for free of their slimy's, these evolution will give access to more and more prices, token and other things in the future...
